title: Welcome - Chinese Hospital
author: Chinese Hospital Editor
description: Based in San Francisco, Chinese Hospital is a community-owned, non-profit community hospital with a rich history that dates back to the late 1800's. Our mission is to provide culturally competent, affordable health care to the community. We feel a deep sense of pride and commitment to all those who place their trust in our care.
